over5 NEWS -- history of user-visible changes.  2002-05-07

Please send over5 bug reports to <over5@kahlin.net>.

Version 0.712

* memslave is now runtime(!) relocatable.

* memslave has the option to install a reset server.

* the VIC-20 version of fastrs is now completely relocatable.

* fixed the bug that prevented SIMPLEREAD working on Win32 systems.

* fixed the bug that required the current directory to be writeable
  when running over5 in server mode. 

* autoconf support, works on atleast Unix systems and Win32 systems
 (using MinGW32)

* completely new directory structure

* added this NEWS file and a ChangeLog

